<plot>This documentary traces the descendants of Spanish Jews who were forced to either flee or convert to Catholicism after Queen Isabella's edict of 1492. Many of these Jews had to practice their religion in secret, passing their furtively-recalled customs down through the generations.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?185942</url></doc>
